+ Type variable name
- camel case = cartItem
- kabeb case = cart-item
- pascal case = Cartitem

+ clear localStorage press: 
- localStorage.clear() 
- localStorage.removeItem('cart')

+ each files can use only one export default

+ 3 main ideas of javaScript:
1, save the data (Model)
2, gerate to html
3, make it interactive

+ update and generate data 
1, update the data
2, generate all the html
Popular technique in software engineering =  MVC : Model-View-Controller
- Model : save and manage the data. Ex: const cart = [{..}], function manageCart () {..}
- View : take the data and displays it on the page. Ex: cart.forEach(..), document
- Controller : run some code when we interact with the page. Ex: button.addEventListener('click' () => {..})
+ MVC is a design pattern

+ framework for testing name 'jasmine'
+mock is the fake vertion use to test on jasmine with 'spyOn'

+ backend 
- 4 types of requests
. Get : get somthing from backend
. Post : create 
. Put : update
. Delete : delete somthing  

